ps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Billy-Corgan-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Billy-Corgan-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Billy-Corgan-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Billy-Corgan-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Billy-Corgan-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Smashing-Pumpkins">Smashing Pumpkins</a>乐队主唱<a href="/artists/Billy-Corgan">比利·科根 (Billy Corgan)</a>分享了洛杉矶山火的镜头，这场山火已迫使超过 15 万居民及更多人离开家园。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">娱乐界对“令人心碎”的洛杉矶野火的反应</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位“1979”歌手以展示他阳台上的景色开始他的视频。科根（Corgan）澄清了巨大的灰色云层实际上并不是云，而是正在进行的破坏性野火中烟雾，这些野火占据了该州数十万的房屋。</p><p> “我想今天给每个人提供一点信息，我感觉好多了。谢谢您的所有良好祝福。但是，嗯，是的，我现在在洛杉矶，这是启示录。我认为昨晚建造了1000个建筑物。我认识的人我必须撤离，这是一个非常激烈的情况，”他说。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEnHTvFpqDE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div>